          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1581614384328-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>king</strong> <strong>prawn mie goreng </strong>with the<strong> remaining speedy sambal</strong> drizzled all over the top</p><p>Garnish with your <strong>crispy onions</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
